### Wayle Configuration - Cava Module

## Audio Processing

settings-modules-cava-bars = Bar Count
    .description = Number of frequency bars

settings-modules-cava-framerate = Framerate
    .description = Visualization update rate in frames per second

settings-modules-cava-stereo = Stereo
    .description = Split bars between left and right audio channels

settings-modules-cava-noise-reduction = Noise Reduction
    .description = Noise reduction filter strength (0.0 fast/noisy to 1.0 slow/smooth)

settings-modules-cava-monstercat = Monstercat Smoothing
    .description = Smooth falloff across adjacent bars (0.0 = off)

settings-modules-cava-waves = Wave Smoothing
    .description = Wave-style smoothing count (0 = off)

settings-modules-cava-low-cutoff = Low Cutoff
    .description = Low frequency cutoff in Hz

settings-modules-cava-high-cutoff = High Cutoff
    .description = High frequency cutoff in Hz

settings-modules-cava-input = Input Method
    .description = Audio capture backend

settings-modules-cava-source = Source
    .description = Audio source identifier (use "auto" for automatic selection)

## Visualization

settings-modules-cava-style = Style
    .description = Visualization rendering style (bars, wave, or peaks)

settings-modules-cava-direction = Direction
    .description = Bar growth direction relative to bar edge

settings-modules-cava-color = Color
    .description = Visualization color

settings-modules-cava-bar-width = Bar Width
    .description = Width of each frequency bar in pixels

settings-modules-cava-bar-gap = Bar Gap
    .description = Gap between frequency bars in pixels

## Container

settings-modules-cava-internal-padding = Internal Padding
    .description = Padding at the ends of the visualizer in rem

settings-modules-cava-button-bg-color = Background Color
    .description = Module background color

settings-modules-cava-border-show = Show Border
    .description = Display border around the visualizer

settings-modules-cava-border-color = Border Color
    .description = Border color token
